    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eyes of Rain is a dark fantasy game where your decisions shape the world's future. Choices can have immediate effects or accumulate over time, leading to endings that range from tragic to resolute.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272510/extras/2f5c34addaebc0612b5c9596078a845b.webp?t=1754784093\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272510/extras/7472ab5ad422bead4f78f88ab3632c37.avif?t=1754784093\" width=600 height=325 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(Primary player character)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A baker in a small, uneventful town, your world shifts when a mercenary in dark clothing shows up to buy a small treat. Who is she? What does she want from you?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272510/extras/0f1c64c8f2965cf394bcfebc0ff07b00.avif?t=1754784093\" width=600 height=325 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Repeated tragedies in her past have led Keniva to accept an endless contract of violence in order to protect what she most holds dear.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272510/extras/bbf0e408e9a388d43a66ecbdc69e3e08.webp?t=1754784093\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eyes of Rain is a dark fantasy visual novel. The branched storyline and how other characters react to you will change in both minor and major ways pending your choices during the adventure. Romance is optional outside of Keniva's Journal, as those unchangeable events have already come to pass.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272510/extras/4ed3f52bdf15b002598e23e2b1a2cea8.webp?t=1754784093\" width=600 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272510/extras/1c7f066298ca1a02c6547a71dea609d7.poster.avif?t=1754784093\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272510/extras/1c7f066298ca1a02c6547a71dea609d7.webm?t=1754784093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272510/extras/1c7f066298ca1a02c6547a71dea609d7.mp4?t=1754784093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive Storytelling: Rich lore in a branching narrative set in the Ethikai universe </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complex Characters: A diverse set of hand-painted fantasy characters ranging from the demonic to the godly, each with their own motivations and secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choice-Drive Gameplay: Your decisions shape the story and influence the world and characters around you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Storylines: As the main storyline progresses, pages of Keniva's journal unlock to reveal her past </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collapsible UI: Hide most of the interface at will for a cleaner view</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Save Slots: Easily save and revisit multiple moments in the storyline to see how things change if decisions are altered</p></li></ul>",
